Battera::

She saw him narrow his optics at her.  She couldn't give away her 
identity. She narrowed her optics at Perceptor. "If your looking at 
me like that, then perhaps I was wrong."  She tilted her head back 
and turned her gaze to the wall, but keeping him in her perifferal 
vision should he make a move towards her.
